#: templates/website/about-branded.html:22
msgid ""
"If you just want to link to WriteToThem to tell other people about it, that&rsquo;s <a href=\"https://www.writetothem.com/about-linktous\">easy</a>. \n"
"\n"
"But maybe you want something shinier than that &ndash; you&rsquo;ve designed a brand new website for your campaign, you want people to write to their MPs to encourage them to support it, and you&rsquo;d absolutely love this to happen without people needing to leave your website at all.\n"
"\n"
"Great news! Someone has written a little application that allows you to do\n"
"this, called WriteToMP. It can look exactly like the campaign&rsquo;s website\n"
"&ndash; it uses WriteToThem to send the message without the user ever needing\n"
"to know what&rsquo;s making that happen.\n"
"\n"
"Before you start, make sure you read our <a href=\"/about-guidelines\">guidelines for campaigners</a>. You must not give your users pre-written messages to send &ndash; they are against our conditions of use and we will block them. \n"
"\n"
"The great thing about this application is that it allows you to suggest the points that you&rsquo;d like people to make when they write their message, but also stresses that they must write in their own words and explains why this is important.\n"
"\n"
"Ready to have a go? <a href=\"https://github.com/robinhouston/write-to-mp\">Here&rsquo;s where you can get the code</a>. \n"
"\n"
"Make sure you read all the instructions on that page &ndash; it should be fairly self-explanatory and you don&rsquo;t need very much technical knowledge to get it working.\n"
"\n"
"If you have any problems installing the code, <a href=\"/about-contact\">contact us</a> and we&rsquo;ll give you a hand."
msgstr ""

#: templates/website/about-campaigns.html:3
msgid "Using  WriteToThem to run a campaign"
msgstr ""

#: templates/website/about-campaigns.html:15
msgid "Running a campaign"
msgstr ""

#: templates/website/about-campaigns.html:23
msgid ""
"Are you part of a campaigning organisation? If you ever ask your supporters to write to politicians, you should know that WriteToThem can be integrated into your website simply, and for free.\n"
"\n"
"All your supporters need do is input their postcode and compose their message, then we send it off to the correct representative. \n"
"\n"
"There are several different options when it comes to using WriteToThem for your campaign. But before we get onto that, a quick word about how WriteToThem <i>can&rsquo;t</i> be used.\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"<li> WriteToThem is <b>not a petitioning site</b>. If you need to collect signatures on a petition and then send it to an MP, you&rsquo;d be better off with one of the many free online petition websites. </li>\n"
"\n"
"<li>We <b>don’t give out MPs’ contact details</b>. Direct email and postal addresses for most MPs can be found on\n"
"<a href=\"http://www.parliament.uk/mps-lords-and-offices/mps/\">Parliament’s website</a> or via the\n"
"<a href=\"http://everypolitician.org/\">EveryPolitician</a> project.</a>.</li>\n"
"\n"
"<li>WriteToThem cannot be used for sending out <b>identically-worded messages</b> from multiple supporters - our system will detect them and block them from being sent.</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"
"Before making the decision to use WriteToThem for your campaign, we&rsquo;d urge you to <a href=\"/about-guidelines\">read our guidelines</a>, and make sure that it fits your needs.\n"
"\n"
"With that said, we&rsquo;re more than happy to provide a free service for campaign groups to encourage people to write to their representatives on a particular issue, and there are a number of ways that you can integrate the WriteToThem experience with your campaign."
msgstr ""

