#: templates/website/about-privacy.html:181
msgid "Retention policies"
msgstr ""

#: templates/website/about-privacy.html:186
msgid ""
"We store your IP address and the pages that you visited whilst on the\n"
"                        site as part of our site logs. We keep these for one month."
